parameters:
My my... well well... I was wondering why the little demons
were so noisy, and it turns out you two are the cause...

Are you the leader of these little demons? The master of
this hideout, perhaps.

Ufufu... Calling me 'you' is quite rude, isn't it? My name
is Yegiku—I've been entrusted with the task of deploying
demons in Edo.
A task...? Who is the leader of you demons? Answer me!

Oh my? You're getting quite heated... Could it be that
you're comrades of the ninjas who were annihilated half a
year ago?

That's right! Most of my comrades, including the former head
of the Iga Ninja, were mercilessly killed! They died a
regrettable death in battle! Prepare yourself!

Hmm... how pitiful... Well then, I'll send you to join your
comrades. Being alone is lonely, after all...

~~~~! Don't play around! I'll sever that white neck of
yours!

Wait a moment, Yugiri-chan! I want to extract information
from this demon! Why did you abduct so many courtesans?

We demons, you see, cannot maintain our immortality without
consuming humans. And what could be better for beauty,
health, and nourishment than the soft and delicious flesh of
women? That's all there is to it--
--t! To treat human life in such a way...!

Unfortunately, as you can see, I am not human. Preaching
human morality to me is futile. Ufufufu♪ The flesh of those
courtesans was quite delicious\I[15]Your youthful flesh
seems like it will be satisfying as well.

It seems we absolutely must defeat this opponent...
Understood. I'll use all my strength to defeat you, a demon!

...Oh? You look familiar... There was someone similar long
ago... A beautiful shrine maiden... Her name was... um...
Shut up, you cur! I won't let you breathe any longer! Die!
Ufufu-- That one is a figure made of ice♪

You're so rough♪ Attacking while I'm speaking... You're a
bad child. A very bad child indeed--

--! The horns are as red as fresh blood...!? Different from
other demons!

A demon with red horns is ten times stronger than a normal
demon. It's fair to call him a demon general. Fight with
caution, Karin--I will naturally stake my life as well!

Really, those little demons are so careless. Letting
intruders easily through to my room... I'll need to punish
those children later♪

(This female demon is overwhelmingly stronger than the
little ones...! If we let our guard down, we'll be done for!
We must fight with all our might!)

Naughty children need to be punished thoroughly! Ufufufu!
Ahahahaha--!!
Ugh--! Ahh...! My body is... hot...!
This is the end for you! Taste my secret sword technique!!
We did it! You're amazing, Yugiri-chan!

The grudge of those you slaughtered is here. I will take
your life. Prepare yourself--

Gah... I was careless... To think you could defeat me... You
both are quite skilled... But... I am the least experienced
among those of us...
Those of you...? Are there others with you?

Yes--compared to me, they are true masters--do not
underestimate them...

...Ah... I remember now, with those sorrowful eyes...
Memories from the past... when I was still human... You
are... Lord Nakatarou's...
--! How do you know my father's name...!?

Ahaha♪ So that's it... You survived. No wonder you bear a
resemblance to that man's wife...
～～～～～～!! You know about my mother too!?
If you don't want to die, survive... Karin...chan...
--Yegiku passed away with a lonely expression on her face...
...Why did this demon know about Karin?

I don't know... That's why I'm shocked... How could a demon
I've never met before know my father's name... and about my
mother too...

<Thump--! Thump--!>(This is the loudest heartbeat sound
ever! What's going on!?

You're the ones who defeated Yegiku after her presence
vanished?

I am the leader of these demons. There's no need for me to
give my name. You will die right here anyway--

Hohoho! How pitiful... How sad... To be defeated by just two
girls, Yegiku.
Yegiku... to think you would die so young among us...

It's a shame. She was the only woman among us [Eight Grudge
War Demons]... How lamentable.

----!! (Such an evil aura...! If I let my guard down even
for a moment, it feels like it could take my entire
consciousness away...!)

We must avenge our comrade, Yegiku. Prepare to die here--are
you ready, dogs of the Shogunate.

Gah--! (Just a light swing of the sword caused this
shockwave...!? )

I shall split you in two with my great sword. Any resistance
will only prolong your agony. Offer your necks willingly.

I know! We can't win against them now! It's frustrating, but
we have to escape!

Oh no you don't. You shall not escape. Fill the skies--my
steel threads--
Uwaaah!? What the!? There are cuts all over my body--!?

Ho ho ho ho! Give up on escaping. I have already cast a
barrier with steel threads that envelop this space. If you
move even slightly, you will slice your own body with the
threads.

~~~~! (No good... They're on a completely different
level...!)

I shall make your death painless by beheading you in an
instant. Close your eyes and pray--die--
Now's the time. Both of you, come to me--
A demon...? One of their comrades...?

...It's been a while. I never imagined we would meet again
under these circumstances.
Traitor! I'll cut off both your hands and feet and kill you!

That won't happen. It's been several decades since I broke
ties with you--I've improved a bit since then. Like this--

Now! While the threads in the air are slack, both of you,
come this way!

--! That woman also has horns on her head! She's a demon
too!? How can we trust her...!

We don't have time for stubbornness right now! If we die, no
flowers will bloom, and we won't be able to avenge
ourselves! We're retreating--!
Thank you for trusting me! Now, grab onto my sleeve--
I will surely shatter your ambitions...
--Karin and Yugiri escaped with the help of the demon girl!

Hoho! How vexing. They managed to escape. Oh dear, what a
blunder, a blunder--

To think that the traitor Kureha would come... It's
regrettable that we, the four War Demons, let the thieves
escape.

Well, it's fine♪ They didn't seem like they were going to
stop fighting, so we'll have another day to meet them again.

Even with Lord Yegiku gone, there are still seven of us
left. There is no significant disruption to our plans. Lord
Kotaro, please give the order to retreat--

...We shall build a grave for Yegiku here before we retreat.
She too shared a long life with us as a comrade in arms...
(...Rest in peace. My fellow villager, Iegiku...)

I thought my heart was going to stop... To be suddenly
surrounded by such monstrous demons...
My name is [Momiji]--I usually live in Edo as a geisha.
Geisha...? Huh? When did your horns...?

Hehe. I can disguise myself by retracting my horns. I
wouldn't be able to live in human society otherwise...

...Are you not a demon as well? Why did you help us humans,
your enemies?
That's because... I was originally human.
...? You mean you were turned into a demon--?

That's right. But it was our own decision. We wouldn't have
survived in that terrible situation otherwise... That's
why...

Yes... Many lives from our village were lost... It was a
dreadful battlefield... It still haunts my dreams...

I can't trust her! She's a demon in human guise...! Demons
are my... enemies! They must all be vanquished... the
detestable beings!

...It's difficult to trust a demon when you've just been
attacked by one. It's only natural to want to attack.
--! (The wound on her cheek, it healed instantly...!? )

...I will disappear for today. The other War Demons are even
more skilled than Lady Yegiku. If you continue to hunt
demons, please be careful. Farewell--

!? Wait a moment, Momiji-san! There's still so much I want
to ask you--!
--Momiji disappeared along with a flurry of cherry blossoms.

Ow ow ow... I have no idea what just happened, but it seems
we've managed to save our skins.

Hmph--to think we'd be saved by a demon after defeating one.
It's hardly a situation that lifts the spirits, is it?

If you're alive, you can fight again and again. Come on,
today's battle is over! Let's prepare for tomorrow's fight.
We'll continue the demon hunt step by step, Yugiri-chan♪

Really... You're such an optimist. Our Iga ninja comrades
must be worried too. Let's head back. I'm getting hungry as
well.

Yeah, let's go home. You can't fight on an empty stomach,
right?♪

--Karin took Yugiri's hand and they started on their way
home.
--\c[17]【Fruit of Attack Power】\c[0] has been obtained!

--Stamina and skill power have been \c[24]fully
restored\c[0]!
